  "instructions": [
    "Heat coconut oil in a saucepan over medium heat until shimmering.",
    "Add minced garlic, ginger, and onion, sauté until onion is translucent.",
    "Stir in turmeric and smoked paprika, cooking for 30 seconds until fragrant.",
    "Add diced plum tomatoes and cook until they soften, about 5 minutes.",
    "Pour in light coconut milk and bring the mixture to a gentle simmer.",
    "Gently fold in cubed tofu and fish sauce, then simmer for 7 minutes, allowing flavors to meld.",
    "Taste and season with salt, adjusting as needed.",
    "Remove from heat and stir in chopped basil.",
    "Serve the stew hot, accompanied by a lime wedge for squeezing.",
    "Enjoy the velvety, comforting stew as a diabetic-friendly dinner."
  ],
